name: NSBitmapImageRep.TIFFCompression
desc: Constants that represent the supported TIFF data-compression schemes.

items.name: case jpeg
items.desc: JPEG compression. No longer supported for input or output.

items.name: case next
items.desc: NeXT compressed. Supported for input only.

items.name: case oldJPEG
items.desc: Old JPEG compression. No longer supported for input or output.
